# Local Development Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your configuration
# .env.local is gitignored and will not be committed

# Application URL (Required)
APP_URL=http://localhost:4201

# ===============================================
# API CREDENTIALS ARE NOW USER-PROVIDED
# ===============================================
# Users configure their API keys in the Settings page of the app.
# No API credentials are needed for deployment!
#
# To use the app:
# 1. Start the development server: yarn start
# 2. Open http://localhost:4201
# 3. Go to Settings
# 4. Enter your API keys from:
#    - Trakt: https://trakt.tv/oauth/applications
#    - MAL: https://myanimelist.net/apiconfig
#    - ids.moe: https://ids.moe/

# Optional: For backward compatibility, you can still set these environment variables
# but they are not recommended in the new architecture
# TRAKT_CLIENT_ID=
# MAL_CLIENT_ID=
# IDS_MOE_API_KEY=
